                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 17.463,
                                "byte_start": 80009,
                                "byte_stop": 149913,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinions of the Court in number 76-1121, American Board Casting companies against the Writers Guild of American, and the two related and consolidated cases will be announced by Mr. Justice White."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 17.463,
